description.narrative:
Overall objective: 

This pilot project is to provide scientific base for planning and facilitating the sustainable development of large-scale mariculture in Quang Ninh. Lessons shall be drawn for other provinces and sub-regions where industrial mariculture is still at the early stage.

Specific objectives:

•	Provide an overall map of Quang Ninh seawater with clear descriptions of potential areas which are suitable for developing offshore mariculture;
•	Provide a detailed assessment of the water carrying capacity in the selected areas (pilot site) for setting up industrial/large scale marine fish farms;
•	Develop a roadmap/strategy for the development of large-scale mariculture in Quang Ninh;
•	Draw the lessons for further application to develop sustainable industrial mariculture in other provinces/sub-regions.
